  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time and historical cryptocurrency price data (50M+ tokens, 940+ exchanges)",
    "DEX analytics — on-chain prices, pools, swaps, liquidity, top traders",
    "WebSocket streaming for real-time price, K-Line, holder, and pool events",
    "x402 pay-per-request protocol — no API key needed, $0.01 USDC per call",
    "MCP server for AI-native integration with Cursor, Claude Code, and Windsurf",
    "Global market metrics — Fear & Greed Index, Altcoin Season Index, CMC 20/100",
    "Real World Assets (RWA) token tracking and issuer data",
    "7 pricing tiers from free Keyless to Enterprise with 30M+ credits/mo"
